  • Method Details

    • getCodeSystemAliases

      public static List<List<String>> getCodeSystemAliases()
      Get a list of aliases known by the V2 Converter for different coding and identifier systems. Returns a list of string lists containing aliases for systems. For each system, the FHIR preferred system URI is first in its sublist, the commonly used V2 namespace is second, and the OID for the system is last.
      Returns:
      A list of string lists containing aliases for a coding or identifier system.

    • toOid

      public static String toOid(String uri)
      Given a URI, get the associated OID
      Parameters:
      uri - The URI to get the OID for
      Returns:
      the associated OID or null if none is known (without the urn:oid: prefix).

    • toTextName

      public static String toTextName(String uri)
      Get the commonly used V2 name for a coding or identifier system.
      Parameters:
      uri - The system name
      Returns:
      The commonly used V2 name, or null if name is unknown.

    • toUri

      public static String toUri(String oid)
      Given a OID, get the associated URI
      Parameters:
      oid - The oid to look up, with or without urn:oid: prefix
      Returns:
      the associated URI or null if none is known

    • getSystemNames

      public static List<String> getSystemNames(String system)
      Get the aliases for any given system.
      Parameters:
      system - The system
      Returns:
      A list of names the system is known by.
